      • addVolunteer

        public boolean addVolunteer(Volunteer newVolunteer,
                            int aSlot)
                     throws MyOwnException
        Add volunteer to a job.
        Parameters:
        newVolunteer - must be Volunteer type and != null.
        aSlot - is a slot name, only 3 options allowed: light, medium, or heavy.
        Returns:

        Throws:
